      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey i was looking through some old declassified documents and certain things just dont add up about the apollo missions. like there are these weird gaps in the public timeline between 69 and the early 70s regarding what they actually saw up there. u think it's possible the official history was basically rewritten to hide something they found?",
